==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frank-marriage
<hw>Frank"-mar"riage</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Frank</ets> free + <ets>marriage</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Eng.
Law)</fld> <def>A certain tenure in tail special; an estate of
inheritance given to a man his wife (the wife being of the blood of the
donor), and descendible to the heirs of their two bodies begotten.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frankness</ent>⟦br⟧
